    "en": {
      "title": "Mano, Hakeem Musteeb to support Dallas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Tamil Progressive Alliance and the Sri Lanka Muslim Congress have decided to support the Dulles beauty in tomorrow's presidential poll in Parliament.",
        "Tamil Progressive Alliance President Mano Ganesan has announced that this decision has been taken after the party meeting held in Nukegodai.",
        "Meanwhile, Sri Lanka Muslim Congress has decided to support Dallas Beauty, General Secretary of the party Nizam Kariapar said."
      ],
